rock - closed fist
paper - a flat hand
scissors - a fist with index and middle finger out

scissors beats paper
    - scissors cut paper
rock beats scissors
    - sometimes blunts scissors
    - breaks scissors
    - crushes scissors
paper beats rock
    - paper covers rock
score system to 3
players
    - 2(user and ai)
outcomes
    win by 3
    if user or computer hits 3 the other opponent loses adding a lost to their win-losses-record
    draw if both users

